statements: SELECT * FROM TrainingData;
SELECT state, action, reward FROM TrainingData WHERE state = 'A';
SELECT id, state, action, next_state FROM TrainingData WHERE reward > 0;
SELECT id, reward FROM TrainingData ORDER BY reward DESC;
SELECT state, COUNT(*) as state_count FROM TrainingData GROUP BY state;
SELECT state, action, reward FROM TrainingData WHERE state = 'A' AND reward > 0 ORDER BY reward DESC
SELECT * FROM TrainingData WHERE action = 'Jump' ORDER BY id ASC LIMIT 10
SELECT state, COUNT(*) as count FROM TrainingData GROUP BY state ORDER BY count DESC
SELECT DISTINCT state, next_state FROM TrainingData WHERE reward < 0
SELECT id, state, action, reward, next_state FROM TrainingData WHERE state IN ('A', 'B', 'C')
SELECT * FROM training_data WHERE reward > 0.5;
SELECT state_vector, reward FROM training_data WHERE data_id = 10;
SELECT action_vector FROM training_data WHERE reward < 0;
SELECT * FROM model_parameters WHERE learning_rate = 0.001;
SELECT model_id, neural_network_structure FROM model_parameters WHERE optimizer = 'Adam';
SELECT * FROM training_data ORDER BY data_id DESC;
SELECT state_vector, action_vector, reward FROM training_data WHERE reward > 0.5 ORDER BY reward DESC, data_id ASC;
SELECT DISTINCT state_vector FROM training_data ORDER BY data_id ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT model_id, neural_network_structure FROM model_parameters WHERE optimizer = 'adam' OR optimizer = 'sgd';
SELECT AVG(reward) AS average_reward FROM training_data;
SELECT * FROM preprocessed_data WHERE id = 1;
SELECT observation, reward FROM preprocessed_data WHERE action = 2;
SELECT id, config_name FROM training_config WHERE optimizer = 'SGD';
SELECT * FROM model_parameters WHERE num_layers > 2 ORDER BY model_name DESC;
SELECT id, optimizer, learning_rate FROM training_config WHERE learning_rate < 0.001;
SELECT * FROM preprocessed_data WHERE action > 5 ORDER BY reward DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT id, observation->>'timestamp' AS timestamp, action, reward FROM preprocessed_data WHERE observation->>'weather' = 'sunny';
SELECT id, config_name, optimizer, learning_rate FROM training_config WHERE optimizer = 'adam' AND learning_rate < 0.001 ORDER BY id ASC;
SELECT model_name, num_layers, hidden_units FROM model_parameters WHERE num_layers >= 3 ORDER BY model_name ASC, hidden_units DESC;
SELECT p.id, p.num_layers, m.hidden_units FROM model_parameters p JOIN training_config c ON p.id = c.id WHERE c.optimizer = 'sgd';
SELECT id, state_vector, reward FROM preprocessed_data;
SELECT model_id, learning_rate, optimizer FROM model_parameters WHERE optimizer = 'adam';
SELECT training_id, training_time, accuracy FROM training_history ORDER BY training_time DESC;
SELECT param_id, parameter_name, parameter_value FROM hyperparameters WHERE param_id > 5;
SELECT id, state_vector, action_vector, reward FROM preprocessed_data WHERE id = 10;
SELECT * FROM preprocessed_data ORDER BY id DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT state_vector, reward FROM preprocessed_data WHERE reward > 0 ORDER BY reward ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT p.model_id, p.optimizer, t.loss FROM model_parameters p JOIN training_history t ON p.model_id = t.model_id WHERE t.accuracy > 0.8 ORDER BY t.loss ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT h.parameter_name, h.parameter_value FROM hyperparameters h WHERE h.parameter_value->>'learning_rate' = '0.01' ORDER BY h.parameter_name ASC LIMIT 3;
SELECT t.training_id, t.model_id, t.training_time FROM training_history t JOIN model_parameters m ON t.model_id = m.model_id WHERE m.layers_count > 3 ORDER BY t.training_time DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM PreprocessedDataForRLModels
SELECT data_column1, data_column3 FROM PreprocessedDataForRLModels WHERE data_column2='value'
SELECT id, reward_value, timestamp FROM Rewards ORDER BY timestamp DESC
SELECT parameter_name, parameter_value FROM ModelParameters WHERE parameter_value='example'
SELECT model_id, history_data FROM ModelHistory
SELECT * FROM PreprocessedDataForRLModels WHERE data_column3 > 100 ORDER BY data_column4 DESC

SELECT MAX(data_column3) AS max_value, MIN(data_column3) AS min_value FROM PreprocessedDataForRLModels
